name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
The leader of the Industrial Securities Sales Department developed an unknown drug and injected it into employees. The whistleblower was fired. Follow-up: 
An informed employee revealed that after the internal public opinion system of the group company detected the exposure, the leader was very angry and threatened to severely punish the whistleblower and send the whistleblower to jail. The leader who illegally injected drugs into employees is still in office and has not received any punishment. The employee who was fired for reporting has not been reinstated.
